description:
Lightweight local memory for your AI agent. SQLite + embeddings, zero setup, no services to run.

Minimal config:
```
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "memory": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "mcp-local-memory"]
    }
  }
}
```

Your agent remembers preferences, project details, procedures -- whatever you want. All structure and behavior controlled via prompts.

For details: [https://github.com/NickSmet/mcp-local-memory](https://github.com/NickSmet/mcp-local-memory)
